<i>noun</i>: 진찰 [진ː찰], 진단 [진ː단], 심사 [심사], 심문 [심문], 수험 [수험], 사열 [사열], 관찰 [관찰], 고사 [고ː사], 검토 [검ː토], 검진 [검ː진], 검사 [검사] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진찰 [진ː찰]</dt><br>
<dd>checkup; examination</dd><br>
<dd>의사가 치료를 위하여 환자의 병이나 상태를 살핌.</dd><br>
<dd>A doctor's act of looking at a patient in order to treat his/her illnesses.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진단 [진ː단]</dt><br>
<dd>1. diagnosis</dd><br>
<dd>의사가 환자를 검사하여 건강 상태를 판단함.</dd><br>
<dd>A doctor's act of examining a patient and determining his/her health.</dd><br>
<dd>2. examination</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상이나 현상에 대해 상태를 판단함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of evaluating the current state of an entity or phenomenon.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>심사 [심사]</dt><br>
<dd>examination; evaluation; screening</dd><br>
<dd>잘하고 못한 것을 가리기 위해 자세히 살핌.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of taking a close look at someone or something to decide whether it or he/she is good or bad.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>심문 [심문]</dt><br>
<dd>interrogation; examination; inquiry</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 사건과 관련된 사람에게 자세하게 따져서 물음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of asking detailed questions to someone related to a certain incident or accident.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수험 [수험]</dt><br>
<dd>examination</dd><br>
<dd>시험을 치름.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of taking an examination.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사열 [사열]</dt><br>
<dd>inspection; examination; scrutiny</dd><br>
<dd>조사하거나 검열하기 위하여 하나씩 살펴봄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of reviewing something one by one for investigation or censorship.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>관찰 [관찰]</dt><br>
<dd>observation; examination</dd><br>
<dd>사물이나 현상을 주의 깊게 자세히 살펴봄.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of watching an object or phenomenon carefully and in detail.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고사 [고ː사]</dt><br>
<dd>examination; test; quiz</dd><br>
<dd>주로 학교에서 학생들의 학업 상태를 평가하기 위해 치르는 시험.</dd><br>
<dd>The test to evaluate the academic achievement of students, usually taken in school.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>검토 [검ː토]</dt><br>
<dd>examination; investigation</dd><br>
<dd>내용을 자세히 따져 봄.</dd><br>
<dd>Reviewing something in depth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>검진 [검ː진]</dt><br>
<dd>examination; checkup; health screening</dd><br>
<dd>건강 상태를 검사하고 진찰하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Testing and examining the state of health.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>검사 [검사]</dt><br>
<dd>examination; inspection</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 대상을 조사하여 옳고 그름이나 좋고 나쁨을 알아냄.</dd><br>
<dd>Reviewing a certain incident or object to decide whether it is right or wrong, or good or bad.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>